HEADWORD: Cric
<hw>Cric</hw> <pr>(kr⟦icr⟧k)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[prob. fr. F.
<ets>cric</ets> a jackscrew.]</ety> <def>The ring which turns inward and
